des: Terri Cole is a licensed psychotherapist, transformation coach, and expert at turning Fear into Freedom. Hello Freedom was created to help people all over the world face their fears, get unstuck from the past, move past their limiting beliefs, and start living the lives they desire. If you enjoyed this episode of Hello Freedom, or you would like to learn more about practical psychology, achieving personal freedom, self-improvement, meditation, mindfulness practices, harnessing the power of intention, and real-life strategies for personal transformation, come visit us at http://www.terricole.com.
